# рџ—„ Database Schema

The database contains the following tables:

- Users
- Artists
- Albums
- Songs
- Playlists
- Playlist Songs
- Listening History
- Subscription Payments
- Payment Audit
- Deleted Payments

---

# рџ“Љ Dataset Summary

| Table | Records |
|--------|---------:|
| Users | 500 |
| Artists | 100 |
| Albums | 62 |
| Songs | 76 |
| Playlists | 1,570 |
| Playlist Songs | 38,907 |
| Listening History | 100,000+ |
| Subscription Payments | 3,921 |

