# в–¶пёЏ How to Run

### 1. Clone the Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/YOUR_GITHUB_USERNAME/Spotify_Music_Analytics.git
```

---

### 2. Open MySQL Workbench

Create a new schema named:

```sql
Spotify_Music
```

---

### 3. Execute SQL Files

Run the files in the following order:

1. schema.sql
2. import_data.sql
3. queries.sql
4. views.sql
5. procedures.sql
6. triggers.sql
7. indexes.sql

---

### 4. Explore the Database

Execute sample queries or call stored procedures to analyze the data.

